# Match .gitignore's build/state carve-outs so `docker build .` context
# stays small on GARM LXD runners. Anything not in git is either
# regenerated by the build stage (node_modules, dist, tunwg) or is a
# per-operator dotfile the image should never inherit.
.git
.github
node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/dist-exe
**/.vitepress/cache
**/*.tsbuildinfo
hub/src/web/embeddedAssets.generated.ts
hub/src/generated
shared/tools/tunwg/tunwg-*
shared/tools/tunwg/*.exe
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/.env*.local
